## Framework Best Practices

### 1. Start Small
Don't create all personas/skills upfront - let the framework grow organically

### 2. Test with AI Agents
Validate documentation by reading as an AI agent would

### 3. Keep Context Manageable
- AGENTS.md: ~200-300 lines
- Skills: ~200-300 lines each
- Personas: ~150-200 lines each

### 4. Version Dependencies
Document versions explicitly: "React 18+" not just "React"

